text.tspan: Arrows on Track 1 and 2 indicate direction of forward locomotive travel.
Clicking the arrow(s) will toggle the bridge direction (i.e. entry vs exit).
Tracks 3-16 will align only to non-cab bridge end (tender closest to turntable).
